f.	FIRST_PROGRAM
 
 Answer: __a, c, f____

9. This is a named storage location in the computer's memory.
a.	class
b.	keyword
c.	variable
d.	operator

  Answer: __c____


10.This keyword is used to declare a named constant.
a.	constant
b.	namedConstant
